<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>EMA625_02_IH_0001</title>

		<!-- 공통 js-->
		<script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
		<script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

		<!-- 공통 css-->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

		<!-- 개별 -->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema625_02.css" />
	</head>

	<body>
		<div id="app_wrap" class="ema624_01_ih_0004 paging">
			<section class="title type2 score">
				<h2 data-head="1_light_purple" lang="y">
					정육각형과 정사각형의 둘레를 이용하여 원주와 지름의 관계를 알아보려고 합니다. 물음에 답해 보세요. 
				</h2>
			</section>

			<section class="contents paging_layout">
				<article class="page page_1">
					<h3 class="title">
						<span lang="y">원주와 정육각형의 둘레, 원주와 정사각형의 둘레를 비교하여</span>
						<span class="circle_blank"></span>
						<span lang="y">안에</span>
						<img src="./../../common_contents/common/img/icon_arrow_right.svg" alt="크다" /><span
							class="ml-10"
							>,</span
						>
						<img src="./../../common_contents/common/img/icon_equal.svg" alt="같다" /><span class="ml-10"
							>,</span
						>
						<img src="./../../common_contents/common/img/icon_arrow_left.svg" alt="작다" />
						<span lang="y"> 중 알맞은 것을 고르세요.</span>
					</h3>

					<div class="question_box justify_center">
						<div class="img_area">
							<img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA625_02_IH/0001_bg.png" alt="" />
							<div class="text_area">
								<div class="text_row">
									<span>(정육각형의 둘레)</span>
									<div class="dropdown_wrap">
										<select class="custom_dropdown math_symbol" data-answer-single="&lt;">
											<option></option>
											<option value="&gt;">&gt;</option>
											<option value="=">=</option>
											<option value="&lt;">&lt;</option>
										</select>
									</div>
									<span>(원주)</span>
								</div>
								<div class="text_row">
									<span>(원주)</span>
									<div class="dropdown_wrap">
										<select class="custom_dropdown math_symbol" data-answer-single="&lt;">
											<option></option>
											<option value="&gt;">&gt;</option>
											<option value="=">=</option>
											<option value="&lt;">&lt;</option>
										</select>
									</div>
									<span>(정사각형의 둘레)</span>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<!-- 해설 -->
					<div class="solve_area">
						<div class="inner_solve">
							<div class="flex">
								<strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
								<div class="conts_solve">
									<p lang="y" class="text_bullet">해설 수급 필요</p>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="buttons_solve"></div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<!-- <div class="btn_area">
						<button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
						<button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
						<button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
					</div> -->
				</article>
				<article class="page page_2">
					<h3 class="title">
						<span lang="y"> 원주와 지름의 관계를 알아보려고 합니다.</span
						><span class="empty_box nemo"></span>
						<span lang="y" class="ml-10">안에 알맞은 수를 써넣으세요.</span>
					</h3>

					<div class="question_box justify_center">
						<div class="img_area">
							<img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA625_02_IH/0001_02.png" alt="" />
							<p class="text1">2 ㎝</p>
							<p class="text2">2 ㎝</p>
						</div>
						<div class="input_area">
							<img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA625_02_IH/0001_02_bg.png" alt="" />
							<div class="text_area">
								<div class="text_row">
									<span lang="y">(정육각형의 둘레)=(원의 지름)×</span>
									<div class="input_wrap">
										<math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="text_row">
									<span lang="y">(정사각형의 둘레)=(원의 지름)×</span>
									<div class="input_wrap">
										<math-field data-answer-single="4"></math-field>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="text_row">
									<img
										class="arrow mr_10"
										src="./../../common_practice/common/img/icon_arrow_right_navy.svg"
										alt=""
									/>
									<span lang="y">(원의 지름)×</span>
									<div class="input_wrap">
										<math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
									</div>
									<span lang="y">&lt; (원주)</span>
								</div>
								<div class="text_row">
									<span lang="y">(원주)&lt;(원의 지름)×</span>
									<div class="input_wrap">
										<math-field data-answer-single="4"></math-field>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- 해설 -->
					<div class="solve_area">
						<div class="inner_solve">
							<div class="flex">
								<strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
								<div class="conts_solve">
									<p lang="y" class="text_bullet">해설 수급 필요</p>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="buttons_solve"></div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</article>
				<div class="btn_area">
					<button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
					<button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
					<button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
				</div>
			</section>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
